---
import { Mail, MapPinned } from 'lucide-astro';
const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, "");
---

<footer id="contacto" class="bg-cards-bg border-t border-grey-100">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 md:gap-9 px-4 md:px-10 py-8 md:py-10 max-w-[1000px] mx-auto w-full">

    <!-- Tarjetas -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-10 items-stretch w-full">

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div data-animate
           class="bg-white border border-grey-50 rounded-xl flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 p-5 md:p-4 flex-1">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 md:gap-4 w-full">
          <img src={`${b}/icons/mail.png`} alt="" aria-hidden="true"
            class="w-[28px] h-[24px] md:w-[35px] md:h-[29px] object-contain shrink-0" />
          <h3 class="font-heading text-type-20 md:text-type-27 text-grey-800 text-center leading-none">
            ¿Quieres que trabajemos juntos?
          </h3>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-type-16 text-grey-500 text-center leading-[1.4] w-full">
          He trabajado con organizaciones de la sociedad civil, ONGs, centros de investigación,
          periodistas y el sector público.{' '}
          <strong>¿Provienes de alguna organización social y te gustaría desarrollar un producto
          usable o comunicar de manera didáctica tus datos?</strong>{' '}
          <a href="mailto:valeria@labtecnosocial.org" class="text-green-600 underline font-bold">
            ¡Mándame un mensaje!
          </a>
          {' '}🌱
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Contacto -->
      <div data-animate style="--anim-delay:120ms"
           class="bg-white border border-grey-50 rounded-xl flex flex-col gap-4 p-5 md:p-4 shrink-0 w-full md:w-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <Mail size={24} class="text-green-600 shrink-0" />
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 font-body">
            <p class="font-bold text-type-12 text-grey-800 leading-[1.2]">Correo electrónico</p>
            <p class="text-type-16 text-grey-500 leading-[1.2] break-all">valeria.peredorodriguez@gmail.com</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <MapPinned size={24} class="text-green-600 shrink-0" />
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 font-body">
            <p class="font-bold text-type-12 text-grey-800 leading-[1.2]">Ubicación</p>
            <p class="text-type-16 text-grey-500 leading-[1.2]">Cochabamba, Bolivia.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Redes -->
    <nav aria-label="Redes sociales">
      <ul class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-5 md:gap-7 list-none font-heading text-type-20 md:text-type-27 text-grey-500">
        <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/valeria-peredo-771765141/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-green-600 transition-colors no-underline">LinkedIn</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@valuka2017" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-green-600 transition-colors no-underline">YouTube</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@valep2017" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-green-600 transition-colors no-underline">TikTok</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/valuka2017/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-green-600 transition-colors no-underline">Instagram</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/valeriaivanna.peredorodriguez/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-green-600 transition-colors no-underline">Facebook</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

  </div>
</footer>
